  "texts": [
    "In line with the sobering AUC value given in Fig. 4, we see in Fig.",
    "6 that the generator requires correction weights essentially all over phase space.",
    "The first distinctive failure mode is corrected by small weights in the energy distributions, for instance in layer 0, which suppress the generated showers to reproduce the sharp lower edge of the energy deposition.",
    "In addition, the network produces too many showers with exactly zero energy deposition in layers 1 and 2 (see App.B).",
    "They are included in an overflow bin in the energy histograms, but appear as a failure mode in the energy fraction of the brightest voxel, for example in layer 2."
  ],
